text: is there any chance to avoid the message "Excel completed file level validation and repair. Some parts of this workbook may have been repaired or discarded." when i create an xlsx file with poi-ooxml?

text:
You won't get an answer until you describe how you build the document that causes Excel to report this as it is caused by an Excel file with incorrect content.

Ideally provide a self-contained unit test which produces the incorrect file so others can reproduce the problem.
No answer for quite some time, therefore closing this for now.
